dc_description_s: This line data layer represents hydrography for Trempealeau County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Trempealeau_HydroLine_2017.gdb.[Rivers, streams, and creeks]
uw_supplemental_s: For complete metadata documentation and online dataset download, please visit http://www.tremplocounty.com/tchome/landrecords/data.aspxAugmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.
